    <td class="rowodd" valign="top" width="2000">1. Previously opened folds are now remembered again. I accidentally broke this in another version.<br>2. The script now can fold abstract classes too. Thanks to Stefan Walk for adjusting the regex.<br>3. Changed behaviour and fixed a bug in searching for trailing empty lines.<br>4. Correct folding of nested folds will be supported in the *next* version.<br>5. Changed some default settings.</td>
</tr>
