    <td class="rowodd" valign="top" width="2000">1. The sequence of creating the custom folds no longer matters.<br>2. Added some more custom folds (includes, defines, .. with phpdoc can now be folded too).<br>3. It can search farther for PhpDoc comments.<br>4. It can be configured to fold more empty 'trailing' lines.<br>5. Adjusted PHPFoldText a bit. <br>6. Fixed a minor bug in the class fold regex (PEAR's QuickForm.php works now too).</td>
